choices.text:
when I was 6, my sister was half my age. Now I am 80. How old is my sister now?
When you were 6 years old and your sister was half your age, she would have been 3 years old. If you are currently 80 years old, then your sister's current age can be calculated by adding the number of years between when you were 6 and now (74) to her original age at that time (3). Therefore, your sister is currently 77 years old.
